data.title: Tank Mayberry - Men's Basketball
data.meta_description: Tank  Mayberry (50) Center  - 2014-15 (Senior): Had five points and five rebounds with three assists and two blocks in 17 minutes of action against St. Gregory's
data.text:
2014-15 (Senior): Had five points and five rebounds with three assists and two blocks in 17 minutes of action against St. Gregory's (11/14)... Scored six points and grabbed a team high eight rebounds with one block against USAO (11/15)... Scored 10 points and grabbed six rebounds with two blocks against NWOSU (11/22)... Collected 4 points, 5 rebounds, and a block against Arkansas Tech (11/25)... Had 8 points, 6 rebounds, 2 blocks, and 1 steal against ECU (11/29)... Against Bacone he recorded 7 points, 7 rebounds, 1 block, and 1 steal (12/16)... Grabbed 9 rebounds and scored 8 points at Southern Nazarene (12/19)... Had a career high 4 blocks against Eastern New Mexico (1/7)... Got a career high of 2 steals against Midwestern State while also scoring 10 points aand coming down with 9 rebounds (3/5).

2013-14 (Junior): In his first game in the black and gold against OPSU (11/8), he had 11 points and eight rebounds... Recorded another 11 and eight performance against NW Oklahoma (11/13) and added three blocks on defense... Scored 10 points and brought down three offensive boards against Oklahoma Christian(12/7).

at USTA: Played in 13 games, while averaging 5.7 minutes ... grabbed a season high four boards in 10 minutes of action at Texas A&M-Corpus Christi on 12/21/12 ... season high 11 minutes against Denver with three rebounds.

at Navarro College: 23 games as a redshirt freshman in 2011-12 ... tallied 43 points (1.9 ppg), 52 rebounds (2.3 rpg) and six blocks ... shot 75 percent (9-12) at the free-throw line ... helped the Bulldogs to a 25-11 record, the Region XIV Tournament Championship and an NJCAA Tournament appearance ... redshirted his true freshman season at Navarro in 2010-11.

High School: averaged 16 points and eight rebounds per game as a senior at Corpus Christi John Paul II High School ... helped lead the Centurions to the TAPPS state semifinals in his final campaign ... was rated a two star recruit and 37th ranked center in the country by ESPN recruiting services.

Personal: Full name is Triton L. Mayberry ... born on July 11, in Corpus Christi, Texas ... son of Sam Gilmore and Tabithttp://www.cameronaggies.com/boxscore.aspx?path=mbball&id=1316ha Mayberry ... has one brother, Shaquille, and two sisters, Sara Vaughn and LaTrenda Vaughn.
